Detailed Description

Structure to store full ephemeris data.

This struct contains comprehensive ephemeris data. This struct is a superset of the RXN_ephem_t struct. Functions exist to convert vars between this struct and RXN_ephem_t (defined within RXN_API.h). Some values are scaled to ICD-200. When this is the case, the scale factors are provided.

Field Documentation

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::af0

Clock Bias Correction Coefficient. Scale: 2^-31. Units: sec.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::af1

Clock Drift Correction Coefficient. Scale: 2^-43. Units: sec/sec.

S08 RXN_FullEph_t::af2

Clock Drift Rate Correction Coefficient. Scale: 2^-55. Units: sec/sec^2.

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::AODO

Age Of Data Offset.

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::CAOrPOnL2

Only 2 least sig bits used. Not in RXN std ephemeris struct.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::cic

Amplitude of the Cos Harmonic Correction Term to the Angle of Inclination. Scale: 2^-29. Units: radians.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::cis

Amplitude of the Sine Harmonic Correction Term to the Angle of Inclination. Scale: 2^-29. Units: radians.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::crc

Amplitude of the Cos Harmonic Correction Term to the Orbit Radius. Scale: 2^-5. Units: meters.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::crs

Amplitude of the Sine Harmonic Correction Term to the Orbit Radius. Scale: 2^-5. Units: meters.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::cuc

Amplitude of the Cos Harmonic Correction Term to the Arguement of Latitude. Scale: 2^-29. Units: radians.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::cus

Amplitude of the Sine Harmonic Correction Term to the Argument of Latitude. Scale: 2^-29. Units: radians.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::delta_n

Mean Motion Difference from Computed Value. Scale: 2^-43. Units: semi-circles/sec.

U32 RXN_FullEph_t::e

Eccentricity. Scale: 2^-33. Units: N/A - Dimensionless.

S08 RXN_FullEph_t::ephem_fit

Fit interval relating to the fit interval flag. Typically 4 hrs.

U16 RXN_FullEph_t::gps_week

Extended week number (i.e. > 1024, e.g.1486).

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::health

Corresponds to the SV health value. 6 bits as described within IS-GPS-200 Rev D.

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::i0

Inclination Angle at Reference Time. Scale: 2^-31/PI. Units: semi-circles.

S16 RXN_FullEph_t::i_dot

Rate of Inclination Angle. Scale: 2^-43. Units: semi-circles/sec.

U16 RXN_FullEph_t::iodc

Issue Of Data (Clock).

U16 RXN_FullEph_t::iode

Issue Of Data (Ephemeris).

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::L2PData

When 1 indicates that the NAV data stream was commanded OFF on the P-code of the L2 channel. Descrete 1/0.

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::m0

Mean Anomaly at Reference Time. Scale: 2^-31/PI. Units: semi-circles.

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::omega0

Longitude of Ascending Node of Orbit Plane and Weekly Epoch. Scale: 2^-31/PI. Units: semi-circles.

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::omega_dot

Rate of Right Ascension. Scale: 2^-43. Units: semi-circles/sec.

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::prn

Ephemeris PRN or SV. Range 1-32.

U32 RXN_FullEph_t::sqrt_a

Square Root of the Semi-Major Axis. Scale: 2^-19. Units: square root of meters.

S08 RXN_FullEph_t::TGD

Time Group Delay. Scale: 2^-31. Units: seconds.

U16 RXN_FullEph_t::toc

Time Of Clock or time of week. Scale: 2^4. Units: seconds.

U16 RXN_FullEph_t::toe

Time Of Ephemeris. Scale: 2^4. Units: seconds.

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::ura

User Range Accuracy index. See IS-GPS-200 Rev D for index values.

U08 RXN_FullEph_t::ure

User Range Error. Indicates EE accuracy. Units: meters.

S32 RXN_FullEph_t::w

Argument of Perigee. Scale: 2^-31/PI. Units: semi-circles.
